### Expansion

In December 2006, a rather ambitious plan was approved: a $700 million expansion project that would push the convention center westward, all the way to [Broad Street](/Broad_Street_(Philadelphia)). This ambitious undertaking aimed to nearly double the convention space, bringing the total to approximately one million square feet. The expansion was completed in March 2011, adding another layer to this already substantial structure. [6]

